snippet.title: Johnny Depp Is BROKE After Amber Heard Controversy!
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp Is BROKE After Amber Heard Controversy!
Honestly, the Johnny Depp and Amber Heard controversies have turned so many tables that nothing surprises me anymore. From co-stars to lovers to couples to enemies, they indeed intend to be each other’s everything. Insecurities, possessiveness, anger, hunger for wealth, what more is left between them? 
After truckloads of allegations and dark secrets coming out to the public, both Amber Heard and Johnny Depp have lost a lot of respect and fandom. The last time I remember, Amber was exposed lying about being the perfectly gentle and sweet wife of Johnny as Johnny’s team presented a phone recording from the past in which Amber herself admitted to being agitated and hurting her then-husband. 
And more and more accusations against the two, it is pretty hard to understand and trust any one of them. No matter what the actual scenario is, the fact is that the two were toxic together and should have never been together. I hope they learned their lessons! 

If you enjoyed the video, make sure to leave a like and tell us what you thought in the comments!
